From Steve Moseley Subject Re How to act in front of traffic jerks In article Niels Mikkel Michelsen writes From Niels Mikkel Michelsen Subject How to act in front of traffic jerks Date Thu Apr GMT The other day it was raining cats and dogs therefor I was going only to the speed limit on nothing more on my This guy in his BMW was driving meters behind me for meters and at the next red light I calmly put the bike on its leg walked back to this car he rolled down the window and I told him he was a total idiot and the reason why Did I do the right thing It works for I avoid obscenities and try to remain calm cool and collected and try something like You almost just killed me and I'm not moving until you or something more or less benign like I haven't been shot a single time but I don't do it in Texas and I do only do it when there are plenty of witnesses Steve Steve Moseley Microbiology SC Phone University of Washington FAX Seattle WA